Yes, it's three one zero, five five five, six seven eight nine.

Perfect! I've got that down. I will send over the size chart shortly. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

No, that's all for now. Thank you for your help!

You're welcome, Emily! Thank you for reaching out to Fashion Central. Have a great day!
